      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows some noticeable signs of age, including minor scratches, small dents, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear on the upholstery and high-touch surfaces. It is a solid, functional car that is ready for the road, though it lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model.",
