    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard that transcends typical pre-owned expectations. This specimen exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the preserved interior surfaces, confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. We invite serious inquiries for this peerless, investment-grade automobile.",
