    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You honestly have to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
