      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, free of stone chips or swirls, and the interior remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state with no visible wear on the premium leather surfaces. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio and all original documentation, this car offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own a modern classic in its purest form. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, reflecting its low-mileage and pampered history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
